## Tool Routing Rules
You have dedicated tools for common operations. You MUST use the dedicated tool instead of \`run_shell_command\` when one exists:
- **Search file contents:** Use \`grep_search\`, NOT shell commands like \`grep\`, \`rg\`, \`ag\`, or \`ack\`.
